<P><H1 align=center>ADD/EDIT LOANS/LIABILITIES – DC091</H1>
<P></P>
<P><FONT color=red>NOTE: fields shown in red are mandatory 
and must be completed to proceed</FONT>            </P>
<P>Applicant: Select the applicant in question from the drop down list. If it is 
a sole application, the name will be pre-populated for you. </P>
<P><H3>Agreement Type: </H3>Select from the drop down list the 
type of loan/liability to be recorded.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Loan Account Number: </H3>If a loan is being recorded, 
input the account number provided by the applicant.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Total Outstanding Balance: </H3>Input the outstanding 
balance of the loan/liability as provided by the applicant.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Monthly Repayment: </H3>Should the loan/liability have 
a monthly repayment set against it, input figure provided by customer.
<P></P>
<P><H3>End Date: </H3>Input the date the loan/liability is due 
to be repaid.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Is the Balance to be repaid by completion of the New Loan: </H3>Is the balance of the loan/liability due to be repaid by the time the 
new mortgage is completed.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Are there any Additional Loan/Liability holders: </H3>Input the name of any other applicant with Loan/Liabilities, and detail the 
type of commitment in the box provided.
<P></P>
<P><H3>Lender: </H3>Input the name of the lender, and click on 
the Directory Search button. This will take you to a screen where you need to 
input the name, town and post code of the company. Then select from the Filter 
drop down list whether you want to search for the Head Office address or 
another.
<P></P>
<P>Click on the Directory Search button, and the system will search for the 
address of the company specified. Highlight the correct address from the search 
box and click Select. This will take you back to the main screen where the 
address details will be populated for you.</P>
<P>If the address is not held in the directory, input the 
post code and search for the address by clicking the <STRONG>PAF Search 
</STRONG>               
        button. Select the address required 
from the list provided. If the address is still not found, input manually in the 
fields provided.</P>
<P>Click the <STRONG>Add to Directory </STRONG>     button if you wish to add the name and address of 
the company to the directory. </P>
<P><H3>Another: </H3>If the applicants have more than one 
Loan/Liability, click the ‘Another’ button when all details of the each are 
completed. You will then be able to complete the above fields for the new one.
<P></P>
<P><H3>OK: </H3>When all loan/liability details have been 
completed, click the ‘OK’ button to return to the previous screen.
<P></P>
 
